---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import site from '@/lib/site';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Vitamin Shots | Menon Medispa & Wellness | Millburn, NJ"
  description="Vitamin injection shots in Millburn NJ. B12, Glutathione, Biotin, and more. Quick, effective vitamin shots for energy, immunity, and beauty."
>
  <main class="sp" data-slug="vitamin-shots-millburn-nj">

    <section class="sp-hero" aria-label="Vitamin Shots in Millburn NJ">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-hero__grid">
          <div class="sp-hero__content">
            <h1 class="sp-hero__title">Vitamin Shots in Millburn NJ</h1>
            <p class="sp-hero__eyebrow">Quick, Effective Vitamin Injections for Targeted Benefits</p>
            <p class="sp-hero__lead">Our vitamin shots deliver targeted nutrients in a quick, convenient injection. Perfect for clients looking for a fast boost without the time commitment of a full IV drip. From B12 and Glutathione to Biotin, we have the perfect shot for your wellness goals.</p>
            <div class="sp-hero__actions">
              <a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold" href="/consultation">Book Your IV Therapy</a>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-reviews">
              <div class="sp-reviews__avatars">
                <img src="/images/90411e0041df.png" alt="Client review" width="44" height="44" />
                <img src="/images/305afeda5f9a.png" alt="Client review" width="44" height="44" />
                <img src="/images/b95880091b44.png" alt="Client review" width="44" height="44" />
              </div>
              <div class="sp-reviews__text">
                <span class="sp-reviews__stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</span>
                <span class="sp-reviews__count">100+ 5 Star Reviews</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <img class="sp-hero__img" src="/images/651c7c197b52.png" alt="Vitamin Shots in Millburn NJ" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-badges" aria-label="Highlights">
      <div class="sp-container sp-badges__row">
        <p class="sp-badge"><span class="sp-badge__check">&#10003;</span> Quick 5-Minute Treatment</p>
        <p class="sp-badge"><span class="sp-badge__check">&#10003;</span> Immediate Absorption</p>
        <p class="sp-badge"><span class="sp-badge__check">&#10003;</span> Multiple Formula Options</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-plain" aria-label="Formulas">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;">
          <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(1.75rem,3vw,2.25rem);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 1.5rem;">Choose Your Formula</h2>
          <div style="background:#f8f4f0;padding:1.5rem;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-xl);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.4rem;">B12 Vitamin Shot</h3>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);font-style:italic;color:#6a6470;margin:0 0 0.75rem;font-size:var(--text-sm);">The classic energy and metabolism booster.</p>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0 0 0.75rem;line-height:1.7;">Vitamin B12 is essential for energy production, red blood cell formation, and neurological function. Our B12 shot provides an immediate, direct-to-bloodstream dose for fast results.</p>
            <ul style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;line-height:1.8;padding-left:1.5rem;margin:0;"><li>Boosts energy and reduces fatigue</li><li>Supports metabolism</li><li>Improves mood and cognitive function</li></ul>
          </div><div style="background:#f8f4f0;padding:1.5rem;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-xl);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.4rem;">Glutathione Shot</h3>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);font-style:italic;color:#6a6470;margin:0 0 0.75rem;font-size:var(--text-sm);">The master antioxidant for skin brightening and detox.</p>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0 0 0.75rem;line-height:1.7;">Glutathione is your body's most powerful antioxidant. Our Glutathione shot supports liver detoxification, brightens skin tone, and provides powerful antioxidant protection.</p>
            <ul style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;line-height:1.8;padding-left:1.5rem;margin:0;"><li>Brightens and evens skin tone</li><li>Supports liver detoxification</li><li>Powerful antioxidant protection</li></ul>
          </div><div style="background:#f8f4f0;padding:1.5rem;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-xl);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.4rem;">Energy Shot (B12 + Glutathione)</h3>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);font-style:italic;color:#6a6470;margin:0 0 0.75rem;font-size:var(--text-sm);">The ultimate combination for energy and glow.</p>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0 0 0.75rem;line-height:1.7;">Combine the energizing power of B12 with the brightening and detoxifying effects of Glutathione in one convenient shot.</p>
            <ul style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;line-height:1.8;padding-left:1.5rem;margin:0;"><li>Maximum energy boost</li><li>Skin brightening benefits</li><li>Antioxidant protection</li></ul>
          </div><div style="background:#f8f4f0;padding:1.5rem;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-xl);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.4rem;">Glow Shot (Biotin + Glutathione)</h3>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);font-style:italic;color:#6a6470;margin:0 0 0.75rem;font-size:var(--text-sm);">The ultimate beauty shot for skin, hair, and nails.</p>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0 0 0.75rem;line-height:1.7;">Biotin is essential for healthy hair, skin, and nail growth, while Glutathione provides the brightening and detoxifying benefits for a true glow.</p>
            <ul style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;line-height:1.8;padding-left:1.5rem;margin:0;"><li>Strengthens hair and nails</li><li>Brightens skin</li><li>Supports collagen production</li></ul>
          </div><div style="background:#f8f4f0;padding:1.5rem;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-xl);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.4rem;">B-Complex Shot</h3>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);font-style:italic;color:#6a6470;margin:0 0 0.75rem;font-size:var(--text-sm);">Complete B-vitamin support for energy and wellness.</p>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0 0 0.75rem;line-height:1.7;">A complete blend of B vitamins (B1, B2, B3, B5, B6) for comprehensive support of your body's energy metabolism, nervous system function, and overall wellness.</p>
            
          </div>
          <p style="margin-top:2rem;"><a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold" href="/consultation">Schedule Now</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-photos" aria-label="Customer Photos">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-photos__head"><h2>Hear From Our Customers!</h2></div>
        <div class="sp-photos__grid">
          <img src="/images/9ebaca3843d3.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/6c461885a28e.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/823792ea5ead.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/cd675890fe0d.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/2e5d1e68225a.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-plain sp-plain--alt" aria-label="Process">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;">
          <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(1.75rem,3vw,2.25rem);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 1.5rem;">Simple, Relaxing, and Effective</h2>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;">
            <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-2xl);color:var(--color-accent-warm);flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;">01</span>
              <div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.25rem;">Personalized Consultation</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0;line-height:1.7;">Your session begins with a brief consultation with one of our registered nurses. They will review your wellness goals and answer any questions to ensure your treatment is perfectly suited to your needs.</p></div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-2xl);color:var(--color-accent-warm);flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;">02</span>
              <div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.25rem;">Relax and Recharge</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0;line-height:1.7;">Once settled in our comfortable therapy lounge, the IV drip is administered. The process is virtually painless and takes about 45-60 minutes. You can relax, read, or catch up on emails while your body absorbs the nutrients.</p></div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-2xl);color:var(--color-accent-warm);flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;">03</span>
              <div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.25rem;">Feel the Benefits</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0;line-height:1.7;">Many clients report immediate benefits after their session. The nutrients continue to work for days, supporting your body's natural processes and helping you feel and look your best.</p></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-pricing" aria-label="Pricing">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-pricing__head">
          <h2>Book Your IV Therapy</h2>
          <p style="font-style:italic;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">All IV Drips are 500ml. Upgrade to 1000ml for only $25</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sp-pricelist">
          <div class="sp-priceitem">
            <img class="sp-priceitem__thumb" src="/images/651c7c197b52.png" alt="B12 Vitamin Shot" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="sp-priceitem__main">
              <a class="sp-priceitem__title" href="/booking-calendar/b12-vitamin-shot">B12 Vitamin Shot</a>
              <p class="sp-priceitem__sub"></p>
              <a class="sp-priceitem__readmore" href="/service-page/b12-vitamin-shot">Read More</a>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-priceitem__price">Call for pricing</div>
            <a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold sp-priceitem__cta" href="/booking-calendar/b12-vitamin-shot">Request to Book</a>
          </div>
          <div class="sp-priceitem">
            <img class="sp-priceitem__thumb" src="/images/651c7c197b52.png" alt="Glutathione Shot" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="sp-priceitem__main">
              <a class="sp-priceitem__title" href="/booking-calendar/glutathione-vitamin-shot">Glutathione Shot</a>
              <p class="sp-priceitem__sub"></p>
              <a class="sp-priceitem__readmore" href="/service-page/glutathione-vitamin-shot">Read More</a>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-priceitem__price">Call for pricing</div>
            <a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold sp-priceitem__cta" href="/booking-calendar/glutathione-vitamin-shot">Request to Book</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-testimonial" aria-label="What Our Clients Say">
      <img class="sp-testimonial__bg" src="/images/30cfb9e87c60.png" alt="" width="1440" height="626" loading="lazy" />
      <div class="sp-testimonial__overlay"></div>
      <div class="sp-container sp-testimonial__inner">
        <h2 class="sp-script-title sp-script-title--light" style="margin-bottom:2rem;">What Our <em>Clients</em> Say</h2>
        <blockquote class="sp-quote">
          <span class="sp-quote__mark">&ldquo;</span>
          Jennifer is amazing. Her aura and energy makes you feel welcomed and comfortable. Love our sessions! And my girl Rose Marie, the receptionist, is just lovely! I always leave with great joy after seeing them.
          <cite>Alexa C.</cite>
        </blockquote>
        <img src="/images/5be44787b3a9.png" alt="5 Star Google Reviews" width="143" height="74" loading="lazy" style="margin-top:1.75rem;" />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-faq" aria-label="Frequently asked questions">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-faq__card">
          <div class="sp-faq__head"><h2 class="sp-faq__title">Frequently asked questions</h2></div>
          <div class="sp-faq__list">
            <details class="sp-faq__item" open>
              <summary>How long does a vitamin shot take?</summary>
              <div class="sp-faq__answer"><p>Vitamin shots take only 5-10 minutes, making them the most convenient option in our IV therapy menu. You can often get a shot during a brief break without disrupting your day.</p></div>
            </details>
            <details class="sp-faq__item">
              <summary>How long do the effects of a vitamin shot last?</summary>
              <div class="sp-faq__answer"><p>The duration of effects varies by vitamin and individual. B12 benefits may be felt for days to weeks. Glutathione's detox effects typically last 1-2 weeks. For sustained benefits, many clients schedule regular shots as part of their wellness routine.</p></div>
            </details>
            <details class="sp-faq__item">
              <summary>Can I combine multiple vitamin shots?</summary>
              <div class="sp-faq__answer"><p>Yes, many of our shots are designed to complement each other. We offer combination shots like our Energy Shot (B12 + Glutathione) and Glow Shot (Biotin + Glutathione). Our team can recommend the best combination for your specific goals.</p></div>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-cta" aria-label="Get Your Vitamin Boost Today">
      <div class="sp-container sp-cta__grid">
        <div class="sp-cta__copy">
          <h2 class="sp-cta__title">Get Your Vitamin Boost Today</h2>
          <p class="sp-cta__sub">Menon Medispa Millburn NJ</p>
          <p>Schedule your vitamin shot appointment at Menon Medispa in Millburn, NJ for a quick, effective boost of the nutrients your body needs.</p>
          <a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold" href="/consultation">Schedule Free Consultation</a>
        </div>
        <div class="sp-cta__media">
          <img src="/images/b1a819f35921.webp" alt="Menon Office Staff" width="431" height="560" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</BaseLayout>
